Problem Fairly recently I came across this error message on one of my hosts &ldquo;esx.problem.visorfs.ramdisk.full&rdquo;
Fallout While trying to address the issue I had the following problems when the ramdisk did indeed &ldquo;fill up&rdquo;
PSOD (worst case happened only once in my experience) VM&rsquo;s struggling to vMotion from the affected host when putting into maintenance mode. Temporary workaround A reboot of the host would clear the problem (clear out the ramdisk) for a short while but the problem will return if not addressed properly.
